author: Gerry Moriarty
title: Death toll from coronavirus in Northern Ireland rises by ten
description: PSNI steps up action to prevent Easter weekend breaches of social distancing rules
content:
The Norths Public Health Agency (PHA) reported on Friday afternoon that ten more people have died from Covid-19 in Northern Ireland, bringing the total number of deaths to 92.
This is the second highest number of deaths recorded in a day in Northern Ireland.… [+2344 chars]
